  "original_title": "''#GOTAGOHOME'' ; \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d87\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 '\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dba'",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'' '#GOTAGOHOME' ''; 'Kitchen lament' heard in Kohuwala",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The protest, dubbed the 'Kitchen Lament', was held in Kohuwala, Colombo, demanding a solution to the country's economic crisis.",
        "The protest on June 11 was attended by people carrying kitchen utensils."
      ],
